Print an svyfui object

print.svyfui.Rd

Print an svyfui object

Usage

# S3 method for class 'svyfui'
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

an object of class svyfui

...

additional arguments to pass to other print methods

Value

The object, invisibly

Examples

# \donttest{
   fit <- svyfui(Y ~ X, data = svyfosr::sample_df, weights = weight)
